ibus-libpinyin

Intelligent Pinyin engine based on libpinyin for IBus

Description
It includes a Chinese Pinyin input method and a Chinese ZhuYin (Bopomofo) input method based on libpinyin for IBus.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Notes: 
-I am primarily editing src/PYSimpTradConverterTable.h
-You also need fonts-hanazono to see some of the characters
-As of Dec 11, 2017 the logic is set primarily to convert SC to TC. Editing characters
must be from the TC side unless the code logic changes. Looking into it
-I changed the icon name of Bopomofo from "Bopomofo" to "Intelligent Bopomofo" so that it doesn't conflict with
ibus-pinyin (different from ibus-libpinyin)

Install:
~$ sudo apt-get install ibus-1.0-dev sqlite3 libsqlite3-dev libdb-dev libdb++-dev gnome-common libibus-1.0-dev
~$ cd /path/to/project/folder
~$ git clone https://github.com/libpinyin/libpinyin.git 
~$ cd libpinyin && git checkout 0.7.x
~$ ./autogen.sh --prefix=/usr
~$ make && make install
~$ cd .. && git clone https://github.com/stevenpan91/ibus-libpinyin.git
~$ cd ibus-libpinyin && git checkout 1.5.x
~$ ./autogen.sh --prefix=/usr
~$ make && make install